data.title: Andy Williams' Moon River Grill CLOSED/REPLACED, Branson, MO
data.meta_description:
THIS RESTAURANT HAS CLOSED -  SEE LISTING FOR SHORTY SMALLS, NOW OPEN AT THIS LOCATION

Andy Williams' Moon River Grill is one of the premiere dining experiences in Branson, Missouri with an exceptional menu and casual inviting atmosphere. Guests at the Moon River Grill may choose several dining options including an atrium with a beautiful view of Branson and the Ozark Mountains, an outdoor patio perfect for those sunny summer days, and the comfortable dining room complete with live music and Andy's private art collection. The Andy Williams' Moon River Grill features an extensive menu that offers appetizers such as Quesadillas, Bacon-wrapped Grilled Shrimp Skewer, and Baked Artichoke Dip as well as a soup of the day and a nice selection of salads and sandwiches. Entrées include Andy's Favorites such as Stuffed Quail, Deep Dish Lasagna, Pecan Encrusted Trout, and Andy's Petite Tenderloin. Guests rave about Andy's Mom's Famous Chicken Pot Pie! The exceptional service, excellent menu fare, and reasonable prices at The Andy Williams' Moon River Grill has created a loyal following by locals and Branson visitors alike. Guests have been known to return to the restaurant after the shows for dessert and coffee.
